data.title: Princess Tam Tam (Uniqlo Groupe): The latest figures, news and market research on Princess Tam Tam (Uniqlo Groupe)
data.meta_description:
Founded in April 1985 by sisters Loumia and Shama Hiridjee, Princesse tam.tam is a French company specializing in lingerie, homewear and bath.
In 2012, Princesse tam.tam is the second largest French lingerie group after Etam.
Princesse tam.tam develops the design of its models in France and mainly subcontracts the manufacturing in five sites: in Morocco, Tunisia, Portugal for nightwear, in the Indian Ocean and in Asia for corsetry and other products.
The company belongs to the Japanese group Uniqlo
